==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Looseness
<hw>Loose"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state, condition, or
quality, of being loose; <as>as, the <ex>looseness</ex> of a cord;
<ex>looseness</ex> of style; <ex>looseness</ex> of morals or of
principles.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loosestrife</ent>⟦br⟧
